# Scoring Model

| Severity | Penalty |
|--------|--------|
| CRITICAL | -20 |
| ERROR | -10 |
| WARNING | -5 |
| NOTICE | -2 |

Maximum Score = 100  
Minimum Score = 0

---

# Risk Bands

| Score | Risk Level |
|------|------------|
| 95-100 | Excellent |
| 85-94 | Low Risk |
| 70-84 | Moderate Risk |
| 50-69 | High Risk |
| 0-49 | Not Ready |

